            <h5 class="mt-0 mb-1">ShiftLeft SAST Scan <a href="https://github.com/ShiftLeftSecurity/sast-scan" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank" class="badge bg-light text-dark">v.{{SLSCAN_VERSION}}</a></h5>
